Introduction

Younique Unit (Korean: 유니크 유닛; Japanese: ユニークユニット) is a special unit consisted of artists under SM Entertainment.

The unit debuted in 2012 with the song 'MAXSTEP' and the line-up consisting of; SUPER JUNIOR's Eunhyuk and Henry, Girls' Generation's Hyoyeon, SHINee's Taemin and EXO's Luhan and Kai.
